Package: poly-tc8-profile-kiosk
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: OpenPolycom <apt@openpolycom.cc>
Installed-Size: 7
Depends: cage, cog
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Description: TC8 device profile: fullscreen web kiosk
 Metapackage selecting the web-kiosk role for the Polycom TC8 panel: a
 Wayland compositor (cage) driving the cog browser at KIOSK_URL. This is
 the device's default profile; today it pins the same stack the base
 image has always shipped — its purpose is to move profile composition
 into the package repository (see polycom_dev/PROFILES-PLAN.md M1).
